古色的外表，充满艺术质感造形；表面经过多次防锈、防腐蚀处理，色泽光亮、手工精致、造型独特、美观大方。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 22pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 22pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: fuchsia\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"652\" height=\"502\" src=\"/images/upload/Image/1(25).jpg\" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: fuchsia\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: blue\">功夫是中国的传统文化</span><span style=\"color: blue\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: blue\">既可以作为装饰家居的时尚工艺品，又可以提高品味价值及生活情趣。商务礼品</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: blue\">温馨家居</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: blue\">婚庆装饰</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: blue\">豪宅别墅</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: blue\">酒吧会所</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: blue\">艺术场所</span><span style=\"color: blue\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: blue\">古典艺术</span><span style=\"color: blue\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: blue\">古典艺术的魅力，在于历经岁月的洗礼和沉淀，依旧葆有幽雅、高贵、唯美与雍容，并且在今日今时看来，愈发透出精致古朴，非一般现代艺术所能媲美的气质。因为那是一份积淀着历史厚重的磅礴与大气，是千百年来历史长河静静流淌而过留给我们的珍贵财富。</span></span></span></span></p>', 'images/201301/thumb_img/349_thumb_G_1357716124066.jpg', 'images/201301/goods_img/349_G_1357716124452.jpg', 'images/201301/source_img/349_G_1357716124499.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1357716124', '100', '0', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '1358969437', '7', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
